gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-5-23 12:56&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;私樓成交&lt;br/&gt;撰文：陳嘉敏&lt;br/&gt;發布時間：16小時前&lt;br/&gt;最後更新：16小時前&lt;br/&gt;蝕讓成交｜呎價1.8萬買入現1.5萬沽出 觀塘凱滙套3房4年貶值逾210萬&lt;br/&gt;▲ 蝕讓成交｜呎價1.8萬買入現1.5萬沽出 觀塘凱滙套3房4年貶值逾210萬&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;利嘉閣地產將軍澳廣場分行市務經理楊凱俊稱，該行近期促成觀塘凱滙3座低層B室成交，實用面積830呎，套3房連士多房間隔，外望開揚園景。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;更多二手筍盤推介：下一頁&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;外區客心儀屋苑樓齡簇新，可步行至港鐵站，附近配套齊全，加上單位間隔四正合用，議價後以1,270萬元成交，實用面積呎價15,301元。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31935652&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=174240822568301adf08eea4_14591689"/><published>2025-05-23T11:19:28+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>e4c16d80af0ccdf49e060a7922fc32af</id><title>🆘蝕讓成交｜馬鞍山迎海‧駿岸2房呎價1.3萬沽 造價較5年前入價跌近2成</title><updated>2025-05-23T11:20:03+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-23T11:20:03+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572527042"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572527042"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3953409%2F%25E8%259D%2595%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25EF%25BD%259C%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%259E%258D%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E8%25BF%258E%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E2%2580%25A7%25E9%25A7%25BF%25E5%25B2%25B82%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%2591%258E%25E5%2583%25B91.3%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%25B2%25BD%25C2%25A0%2520%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%2583%25B9%25E8%25BC%25835%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%2583%25B9%25E8%25B7%258C%25E8%25BF%25912%25E6%2588%2590%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=9627c42e01e475cf999345d024cab301&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3953 ... 5年前入價跌近2成?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;